text: Saby Natonga (1970) is a Vanuatuan professional football manager and the current Vice President of the Vanuatu Football Federation.Vanuatu on FIFA.com - FIFA.com In 1996 and from July 2011 to May 2012 he was coach of the Vanuatu national football team.Vanuatu prepare for Solomon friendlies - Oceania Football Confederation ==References== ==External links== *Profile at Soccerway.com *Profile at Soccerpunter.com * Part of book of Eric WITTERSHEIM about Vanuatu independence Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Vanuatuan football managers Category:Vanuatu national football team managers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
